latestIgtvVideos.title: @xotikcafe is a cafe that lives up to its name.The ambience is quite nice.
latestIgtvVideos.caption: The food was absolutely wonderful, from preparation to presentation, very pleasing. Especially enjoyed the special  drinks, The food was fresh, properly prepared and a great value for the price. highly recommend it.
